title: "AI Eval Forge: Mixed-Check Regression Testing for LLM and Agent Workflows"
message: "If you use this manuscript bundle, please cite the preprint record once it is published."
type: article
authors:
  - family-names: "Katta"
    given-names: "Mukunda Rao"
repository-code: "https://github.com/MukundaKatta/ai-eval-forge-js"
abstract: "Large-model and agent teams often need faster regression checks than broad benchmark suites can provide. This paper presents AI Eval Forge, a zero-dependency evaluation harness for mixed-check regression testing across LLM and agent workflows."
